Examples below…

Result as Value Type

In the example below the query result is expected to be of non-nullable type double. If the result is null, there will be conversion error(s) of type JsonQL.JsonToObjectConversion.IConversionError in result with value of ErrorType equal to ValueNotSet.

Result as Reference Type

In the example below the query result is expected to be of non-nullable type IEmployee. If the result is null, there will be conversion error(s) of type JsonQL.JsonToObjectConversion.IConversionError in result with value of ErrorType equal to ValueNotSet.
